{"tid":625407,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【特稿】古天奴仲有機會攞歐聯獎牌","createTime":"2018-04-11T12:10:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-11T15:33:16.000Z","uid":1121,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b1086c3722b9aa93157b9f6c5f4d81088edb415a","tid":625407,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T12:10:12.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=60IjaljOmdVCL6an69oRXUzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=4ed393d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】利物浦淘汰曼城闖入歐聯4強，而舊將菲臘比古天奴所屬的巴塞隆拿卻爆冷出局，不過原來後者也有取得冠軍獎牌的資格。<br />\n<br />\n根據歐聯規則，冠軍隊伍可以獲得40面獎牌，然後由球會決定由哪位球員獲分獎牌。如果利物浦最後贏得歐聯冠軍，今季曾經為紅軍上陣5場歐聯比賽的菲臘比古天奴（Philippe Coutinho），雖然已於1月轉投巴塞隆拿，卻因此仍有資格取得歐聯冠軍獎牌，但最後決定權仍落在利物浦手上。<br />\n<br />\n其實菲臘比古天奴離隊後，利物浦依然攻力驚人，更打破曼聯保持的歐聯單季入球紀錄。在8強次回合賽事，羅拔圖法明奴（Roberto Firmino）把握機會奠勝的入球，把紅軍今季在歐聯的入球數字增至33球，打破曼聯在2002/03賽季攻入32球的歐聯單季入球紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n利物浦之後還要面對歐聯4強的賽事，即至少多賽兩場，絕對有機會再度改寫這個紀錄。"},{"pid":"4fa249d13e2311966d07cb888f81235f3e2dd73f","tid":625407,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T12:10:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34680af2646f62208acd4272174fe6a43de4201e","tid":625407,"uid":39012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T12:16:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"001b2824a81761e2e03853ade8071c4b047ee725","tid":625407,"uid":20522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T12:29:00.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97ec8df22ce2df1fe80c6a293423df8ce9e3b35b","tid":625407,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T15:03:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60e01ca32e47f937c4680de637c2bb9865b2d5a1","tid":625407,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T15:10:20.000Z","msg":"最後決定權仍落在利物浦手上。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64cdda5ee9d5ac9ebce656bff20bee9e3a420a27","tid":625407,"uid":13343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T15:33:16.000Z","msg":"我係利嘅話會公開話畀佢（本身都無40個大踢到5場或以上？）<br />\n<br />\n因為古都唔會好意思收<br />\n<br />\n利咁樣反而畀人一個大方嘅形象<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過都係個句<br />\n利記都拎唔到㗎啦<br />\n諗咁多托咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}